OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773027579
OL,3,CGender-affirming hormone treatment for
OL,4,Cchildren halted by NHS
OL,6,FGender-affirming hormone treatment for
OL,7,F16 and 17-year-olds has been paused
OL,8,Fafter an NHS review found evidence
OL,9,Fdoes not support its continued use.
OL,11,FThe treatment, prescribing
OL,12,Fmasculinising or feminising hormones,
OL,13,Fhas been available on the NHS for 16
OL,14,Fand 17-year-olds with a diagnosis of
OL,15,Fgender dysphoria who meet certain
OL,16,Fcriteria, but new referrals have been
OL,17,Fpaused from Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
