FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773027579
OL,3,CGender-affirming hormone treatment for
OL,4,Cchildren halted by NHS
OL,6,FIt is launching a 90-day consultation
OL,7,Fon plans for the NHS to remove the
OL,8,Ftreatment as a routine procedure.
OL,10,FThe treatment will be paused
OL,11,Fthroughout the consultation period and
OL,12,Fwhile NHS England reviews the expected
OL,13,Fthousands of responses before reaching
OL,14,Fa final decision.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
