PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773027580
OL,3,CGender-affirming hormone treatment for
OL,4,Cchildren halted by NHS
OL,6,FA clinical trial into the impacts of
OL,7,Fpuberty blockers on children as young
OL,8,Fas 10, launched in November, was
OL,9,Fpaused last month ` before anyone had
OL,10,Fbeen recruited ` amid concerns about
OL,11,Fthe "unquantified risk" of "long-term
OL,12,Fbiological harms".
OL,14,FUse of the drugs to delay or prevent
OL,15,Fpuberty happening was banned for under-
OL,16,F18s in 2024.
OL,26,@sD@EOUsD@WO]sD@\OUtD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
