PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773027580
OL,3,CGender-affirming hormone treatment for
OL,4,Cchildren halted by NHS
OL,6,FProfessor James Palmer, national
OL,7,Fmedical director for specialised
OL,8,Fservices at NHS England, said:
OL,9,F"Following the Cass Review, NHS
OL,10,FEngland commissioned an in-depth
OL,11,Freview of all available clinical
OL,12,Fevidence for using oestrogen or
OL,13,Ftestosterone either alone or with
OL,14,Fother medications to treat gender
OL,15,Fincongruence and dysphoria.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773027580
OL,3,CGender-affirming hormone treatment for
OL,4,Cchildren halted by NHS
OL,6,F"This review has established that the
OL,7,Favailable evidence does not support
OL,8,Fthe continued use of masculinising or
OL,9,Ffeminising hormones to treat gender
OL,10,Fincongruence or dysphoria for young
OL,11,Fpeople under 18.
OL,13,F"We are now launching a public
OL,14,Fconsultation on a revised policy which
OL,15,Fwould see the NHS remove this
OL,16,Ftreatment as a routine intervention
OL,17,Ffor young people under 18. As part of
OL,18,Fthe consultation NHS England will want
OL,19,Fto determine whether any key evidence
OL,20,Fmay need to be reviewed before a final
OL,21,Fpolicy is published.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773027580
OL,3,CGender-affirming hormone treatment for
OL,4,Cchildren halted by NHS
OL,6,F"The NHS has exercised extreme caution
OL,7,Fwhen considering starting young people
OL,8,Fon this treatment ` in accordance with
OL,9,Fthe advice from Dr Cass ` and as part
OL,10,Fof this action will now be pausing any
OL,11,Fnew referrals for this treatment for
OL,12,F16 and 17-year-olds.
OL,14,F"Patients currently receiving these
OL,15,Ftreatments on the NHS can continue but
OL,16,Fthis will need to be reviewed
OL,17,Findividually with their clinical team.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773027580
OL,3,CGender-affirming hormone treatment for
OL,4,Cchildren halted by NHS
OL,6,F"The NHS continues to offer specialist
OL,7,Fsupport for under-18s managing gender
OL,8,Fincongruence, including mental health
OL,9,Fsupport and referral to specialist
OL,10,Fchildren and young people's gender
OL,11,Fservices where appropriate."
OL,13,FTammy Hymas, policy lead at advocacy
OL,14,Fgroup TransActual, said: "Banning new
OL,15,Fprescriptions of gender-affirming
OL,16,Fhormones for 16 and 17-year-olds is a
OL,17,Fprofound attack on young people's
OL,18,Fbodily autonomy with trans people yet
OL,19,Fagain cruelly singled out by this
OL,20,Fgovernment."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@\O]vD@ZOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773027580
OL,3,CGender-affirming hormone treatment for
OL,4,Cchildren halted by NHS
OL,6,FHelen Joyce, director of advocacy at
OL,7,FSex Matters, said the pause "comes too
OL,8,Flate" for many children.
OL,10,F"Under-18s are simply too young to
OL,11,Fconsent to such irreversible, life-
OL,12,Fchanging consequences," Ms Joyce said.
OL,14,F"This pause now needs to be made
OL,15,Fpermanent, as part of the long road
OL,16,Fback to sanity on gender issues for
OL,17,Fthe NHS."
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@EO]rD@AOUtD@WO]vD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
